{{Year in Mexico|1884}}
Events in the year '''1884 in Mexico'''.

== Incumbents ==
* [[President of Mexico|President]] &ndash; [[Manuel González Flores]] until November 30, [[Porfirio Díaz]] from December 1
* [[Archbishop of Mexico]] &ndash; [[Pelagio Antonio de Labastida y Dávalos]]
{{For|the list of governors of the states of Mexico|Category:Lists of governors of States of Mexico}}

==Events==
* June 2 &ndash; [[Banamex]] was formed from the merger of [[Banco Nacional Mexicano]] and [[Banco Mercantil Mexicano]], two banks that had operated since the beginning of 1882.
* December 1 &ndash; [[Porfirio Díaz]] becomes [[president of Mexico]] for the second time after winning the elections.
* December 18 &ndash; The Territory of [[Nayarit]] is formed once its territorial limits with [[Jalisco]] were established.

